createPDUHeader

public byte[] createPDUHeader()
Convert the values of the header into 20 bytes of encoded Diameter header. Do NOT forget to set the messagelength to HEADLENGTH plus the length of the body.

storeHeader

public void storeHeader(String storeVar,
                        Vector<String> extendedStoreVarValue)
Store the headers in XTT varables, storeVar is the location in front of the variable names, extendedStoreVarValue is a Vector containing additional store name pieces set by the decodeBody on Diamerer_PDUBody according to extendedStoreVar and AVP values.
